  "texts": [
    "Partial equilibrium distributions for a fixed time and different values of the activity level.",
    "Inactive agents are characterized by opinion polarization, while active ones by consensus formation.",
    "In (A) m Ā = 0 while in (B) m Ā = -0.2, the other values are ρ Ā = 0.65, ω p = 0.8, ε = 0.05, and ν p = 0.04.",
